        <h2>Healthy Living Tips</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Drink plenty of water throughout the day to stay hydrated.</li>
            <li>Eat a balanced diet with a variety of fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and lean proteins.</li>
            <li>Get regular exercise to keep your body and mind active.</li>
            <li>Ensure a good night's sleep for overall well-being.</li>
            <li>Manage stress through relaxation techniques like meditation or deep breathing.</li>
            <li>Avoid excessive consumption of sugary and processed foods.</li>
            <li>Practice proper hand hygiene to prevent the spread of germs.</li>
            <li>Engage in activities you enjoy to promote mental and emotional well-being.</li>
            <li>Limit screen time and take breaks to protect your eyes and reduce sedentary behavior.</li>
            <li>Visit your healthcare professional for regular check-ups and screenings.</li>
        </ul>
